Package: lcaStats
Title: Reproducible Statistics for Life Cycle Assessment
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Harper Food Innovation", "Digital",
           email = "placeholder@harper-adams.ac.uk",
           role  = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for statistical analysis in Life Cycle Assessment (LCA),
    starting with the pedigree matrix approach for converting ecoinvent Data
    Quality Indicator (DQI) scores into lognormal uncertainty parameters.
    Provides functions for single exchanges, batch processing of inventory
    tables, Monte Carlo sampling helpers, and an interactive Shiny application.
    Based on the methodology of Weidema et al. (2013)
    <https://www.ecoinvent.org/files/dataqualityguideline_ecoinvent_3_20130506.pdf>.
